{"collection": "listening", "type": "array", "data": [{"id": "xcd_1", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "What are you up to today?", "ja": "今日は何する予定？"}, {"id": "xcd_2", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "Not much, just relaxing.", "ja": "特に何も、のんびりしてる。"}, {"id": "xcd_3", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "Want to grab a bite?", "ja": "何か食べに行かない？"}, {"id": "xcd_4", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "Sounds good to me.", "ja": "いいね。"}, {"id": "xcd_5", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "I'll be there in five.", "ja": "5分で着くよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_6", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "Take your time.", "ja": "急がなくていいよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_7", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "My treat.", "ja": "おごるよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_8", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "You shouldn't have.", "ja": "わざわざありがとう。"}, {"id": "xcd_9", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "No worries at all.", "ja": "全然気にしないで。"}, {"id": "xcd_10", "type": "dictation", "level": "A2", "text": "I owe you one.", "ja": "恩に着るよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_11", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "Do you mind if I tag along?", "ja": "ついて行ってもいい？"}, {"id": "xcd_12", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "The more the merrier.", "ja": "大勢の方が楽しいよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_13", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I'm game if you are.", "ja": "君がよければ乗るよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_14", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "Count me in.", "ja": "参加するよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_15", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I'll pass this time.", "ja": "今回は遠慮するよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_16", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "Maybe next time.", "ja": "また今度ね。"}, {"id": "xcd_17", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "Let's play it by ear.", "ja": "成り行きで決めよう。"}, {"id": "xcd_18", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I'll keep you posted.", "ja": "進展があったら伝えるね。"}, {"id": "xcd_19", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I'm swamped today.", "ja": "今日は超忙しい。"}, {"id": "xcd_20", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I could use a break.", "ja": "休憩が必要。"}, {"id": "xcd_21", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "That slipped my mind.", "ja": "すっかり忘れてた。"}, {"id": "xcd_22", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "It totally skipped my mind.", "ja": "完全に頭から抜けてた。"}, {"id": "xcd_23", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "You read my mind.", "ja": "まさに同じこと考えてた。"}, {"id": "xcd_24", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "Great minds think alike.", "ja": "考える事は同じだね。"}, {"id": "xcd_25", "type": "dictation", "level": "B1", "text": "I'm on the fence about it.", "ja": "まだ決めかねてる。"}, {"id": "xcd_26", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I'm leaning toward yes.", "ja": "前向きに傾いてる。"}, {"id": "xcd_27", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I'm torn between the two.", "ja": "二つで迷ってる。"}, {"id": "xcd_28", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "It's a toss-up.", "ja": "五分五分だね。"}, {"id": "xcd_29", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "That's a tough call.", "ja": "難しい判断だね。"}, {"id": "xcd_30", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Sleep on it.", "ja": "一晩考えよう。"}, {"id": "xcd_31", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Let's not overthink it.", "ja": "考えすぎないようにしよう。"}, {"id": "xcd_32", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Trust your gut.", "ja": "直感を信じて。"}, {"id": "xcd_33", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "What's the worst that can happen?", "ja": "最悪何が起きる？"}, {"id": "xcd_34", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "We'll figure it out.", "ja": "なんとかなるよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_35", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "One step at a time.", "ja": "一歩ずつ行こう。"}, {"id": "xcd_36", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Rome wasn't built in a day.", "ja": "ローマは一日にして成らず。"}, {"id": "xcd_37", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Hang in there.", "ja": "頑張って持ちこたえて。"}, {"id": "xcd_38", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "You've got this.", "ja": "君ならできるよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_39", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I'm rooting for you.", "ja": "応援してるよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_40", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "Break a leg.", "ja": "うまくいくことを祈ってるよ。"}, {"id": "xcd_41", "type": "dictation", "level": "C1", "text": "I'd rather not get into that right now.", "ja": "今はその話に入りたくない。"}, {"id": "xcd_42", "type": "dictation", "level": "C1", "text": "Let's table that for another time.", "ja": "それは別の機会にしよう。"}, {"id": "xcd_43", "type": "dictation", "level": "C1", "text": "I'll defer to your judgment on this.", "ja": "この件はあなたの判断に任せます。"}, {"id": "xcd_44", "type": "dictation", "level": "C1", "text": "I appreciate you flagging that.", "ja": "指摘してくれてありがたい。"}, {"id": "xcd_45", "type": "dictation", "level": "C1", "text": "That's a fair point I hadn't considered.", "ja": "考えていなかった妥当な指摘です。"}, {"id": "xcd_46", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I was wondering if you could proofread this for me.", "ja": "校正してもらえないかなと思って。"}, {"id": "xcd_47", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I was wondering if there's a faster way to do this.", "ja": "もっと早いやり方がないかなと。"}, {"id": "xcd_48", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I was wondering if you had any feedback on my proposal.", "ja": "提案へのフィードバックをいただけないかと。"}, {"id": "xcd_49", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I was wondering if we could move the meeting to Thursday.", "ja": "会議を木曜にずらせないかと。"}, {"id": "xcd_50", "type": "dictation", "level": "B2", "text": "I was wondering if you'd be open to a different approach.", "ja": "別のやり方を検討いただけないかと。"}]}